'''Semapedia'''


URL = http://www.semapedia.org/


=Description=


"Semapedia centres around the notion of making scannable barcode tags and sticking them to physical objects and places, so that camera phone toting travellers can tap into wikipedia while they’re out and about. With Semapedia barcodes stuck to real spaces, the possibility of finding information about said spaces suddenly becomes very easy."
(http://bricolab.com/blog/2006/08/09/semapedia-hooks-wikipedia-up-to-the-world/)


